Constructors:
    Constructor help us give initial values to the fields of a class.

Why we should use a constructor:
    1.Constructor help us write clearer code.
    2.Constructors give us more control over the values that an end user can assign
     to the field of a class.

Syntax of Constructor:
    Access_modifier className (parameters){
    }
    ----------------------
    Class dog{
    String name;
    public Dog(String dogName){
    name=dogName;
    }

    }